      "officialTitle": "A PHASE 2, RANDOMIZED, DOUBLE-BLIND, PLACEBO-CONTROLLED STUDY TO EVALUATE THE EFFICACY AND SAFETY OF AN ORAL BRANCHED-CHAIN KETOACID DEHYDROGENASE KINASE INHIBITOR, PF-07328948, IN ADULTS WITH HEART FAILURE (BRANCH-HF)"
